snippet.title: Star Wars Explained
snippet.description:
Subscribe to see new videos every day covering Star Wars Canon and Legends lore.  I talk about characters, history, ships, technology, aliens, planets, behind the scenes, books, comics, video games, TV, and of course the films.  If it’s Star Wars, you can learn about it here.

Mailing Address

Ste 208 PMB 264
